 dynamics*. By explicitly modeling how evidence integration evolves, EHIR-IRT achieves superior generalization under noise, domain shift, and low-resource settings. It also offers unprecedented interpretability—users can trace not just *what* the model attended to, but *how its understanding changed over time*. Potential impact spans high-stakes NLP applications such as scientific argument mining, legal document analysis, and AI writing assistants, where error cascades are costly and transparency is essential.",
